Title: An Act Naming the Highway Connecting the Municipalities of San Remigio and Tabuelan in the Province of Cebu as Antonio Y. De Pio Highway
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 383
An Act Naming the Highway Connecting the Municipalities of San Remigio and Tabuelan in the Province of Cebu as Antonio Y. De Pio Highway
Section 1. The highway connecting the Municipalities of San Remigio and Tabuelan in the Province of Cebu shall be known as Antonio Y. de Pio Highway.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 8, 1983
